10th Street, west from Fifth Avenue, showing the north side of the street. St. Thomas Aquinas Roman Catholic Church is in the right background.
P. L. Sperr  May 3, 1941

702435f-a.text:
5th Avenue, north from Tenth Street. On the right can be seen the Prospect branch of the Brooklyn Public Library and Public School No. 39.
P. L. Sperr  May 3, 1941
